OL,4,G2245FSean Connery Vs James Bond
OL,5,     GExplore the eclectic career of
OL,6,     GSean Connery, who, having become
OL,7,     Ga star thanks to James Bond,
OL,8,     Gnever stopped trying to shed the
OL,9,     Gimage of a sexy, brutal macho
OL,10,     Gthat stuck to 007.
OL,11,G0000FNothing Compares
OL,12,     GAbsorbing documentary charting
OL,13,     GSinead O'Connor's rise to
OL,14,     Gworldwide stardom and the
OL,15,     Gfearless singer's departure from
OL,16,     Gthe pop mainstream. Features
OL,17,     Gpreviously unseen footage.
